    "description": "Complete test collection for FBS API.\n\nRun order for E2E flow:\n1. Search Flights \u2192 saves flightNumber automatically\n2. Get Flight By Number \u2192 saves seatNumber automatically\n3. Create Reservation \u2192 saves reservationId automatically\n4. Get Reservation \u2192 assert status is Pending\n5. Confirm Reservation \u2192 204\n6. Get Reservation \u2192 assert status is Confirmed\n\nNote on error responses: MapErrorToResponse returns a plain string body, not ProblemDetails JSON.\nError assertions use pm.response.text() accordingly.",
